{"word":"G4649 - σκοπός - skopós - skop-os' - Mark","slug":"G4649","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">σκοπός</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>skopós"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>skop-os'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Mark"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03C3;&#x03BA;&#x03BF;&#x03C0;&#x03BF;&#x0301;&#x03C2; - skopos</b> - <i>skop-os'</i><p/>(&ldquo;scope&rdquo;); From <b>&#x03C3;&#x03BA;&#x03B5;&#x0301;&#x03C0;&#x03C4;&#x03BF;&#x03BC;&#x03B1;&#x03B9;</b> <b>skeptomai</b> (to <i>peer</i> about [&ldquo;skeptic&rdquo;]; perhaps akin to <a href=\"#/G4626\">G4626</a> through the idea of <i>concealment</i>; compare <a href=\"#/G4629\">G4629</a>); a <i>watch</i> (<i>sentry</i> or <i>scout</i>), that is, (by implication) a <i>goal:</i> - mark."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G2684\">G2684</a>, <a href=\"#/G2685\">G2685</a>, <a href=\"#/G4648\">G4648</a>"}]}